data.message: Welcome to the Internet Friends website!
But I'm here to show you what Internet Friends looks like!
Internet Friends is a browser extension
If you're on the same webpage as someone else with the extension, you'll see them, like you see me!
You can open chat by pressing Ctrl + Shift + Enter!
Type your message and press Enter again to send it!
You can change settings, like your color or which sites are enabled, from the extension's action menu
You can also send other people the link to this website now and see them when they arrive!
